            text = "un zog ikh dos iz nisht keyn takhles, bin ikh gegangen, eh ikh bin gevezn in militer, bin ikh gegangen tsu a ofitsir, ikh hob mikh gegebn a shtek UNK, ikh bin geven a RAV-TORI, zog ikh," 
